<p class=3D"MsoFooter" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoFooter" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">MR. EARNEST:&nbsp; Well, =
I don't have any comment to share from the President about ongoing litigati=
on.&nbsp; The President did have an opportunity when he was in Flint to see=
 firsthand the impact this crisis has had on that
 community.&nbsp; The President has made clear he&#8217;s going to mobilize=
 resources from federal government to help that local community.&nbsp; And =
