<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Josh, g=
iven what a deadly it was in Baghdad, are there any plans for the President=
 or perhaps the Vice President to reach out to the Abadi leadership?<o:p></=
o:p></p>
