<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Given n=
ot just today's violence, but the political crisis that's ongoing in Baghda=
d, I mean, does the White House still believe that Abadi is strong, as the =
