<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Last on=
e.&nbsp; Would the President consider backing an idea of partitioning the c=
ountry?<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; MR. EARNEST:&nbsp; Well, th=
ere are obviously people that have floated this idea in a variety of contex=
ts, including even the Vice President in his presidential campaign eight ye=
ars ago.&nbsp; What our policy and our belief continues to be is
