<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; But, of course, at U.S. dip=
lomatic facilities all around the world there are United States Marine Corp=
s servicemembers who are standing guard.&nbsp; And the President takes that=
 security quite seriously, but that certainly does not absolve
